OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,FThomas Tuchel has warned that England
OL,7,Fmust change their football "DNA" if
OL,8,Fthey are to end their long wait for
OL,9,Fmajor tournament success, after a
OL,10,Fpainful semi-final exit at the hands
OL,11,Fof Argentina.
OL,13,FTuchel, who replaced Sir Gareth
OL,14,FSouthgate with the explicit brief of
OL,15,Fgetting them over the line in major
OL,16,Ftournaments, has faced criticism for
OL,17,Fsome early defensive substitutions in
OL,18,FWednesday's match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
