OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,FThe Three Lions were on the cusp of
OL,7,Ftheir first final since 1966 when
OL,8,FAnthony Gordon's 55th-minute goal put
OL,9,Fthem ahead in Atlanta, but they became
OL,10,Fpassive, falling to a predictable 2-1
OL,11,Floss after late goals from Enzo
OL,12,FFernandez and Lautaro Martinez.
OL,14,FIt was the fourth time England had
OL,15,Fretreated in a major knockout match,
OL,16,Fhaving sat back after taking the lead
OL,17,Fagainst Croatia in the 2018 World Cup
OL,18,Fsemi-final and Italy in the Euro 2020
OL,19,Ffinal, while also failing to
OL,20,Fcapitalise on their equaliser against
OL,21,FSpain in the Euro 2024 final.
OL,26,@tD@ErptD@[rt
