OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,FTuchel has been heavily criticised in
OL,7,Fthe aftermath of the semi-final loss,
OL,8,Faccused of negative tactics -
OL,9,Fincluding replacing goalscorer Gordon
OL,10,Fwith defender Ezri Konsa midway
OL,11,Fthrough the second half - which
OL,12,Fultimately led to Argentina's comeback.
OL,14,FBut the England boss has defended his
OL,15,Fformations, saying that the "big
OL,16,Fproblem" is the English football "DNA"
OL,17,Fand how the team struggles to control
OL,18,Fthe game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
