SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,FAsked whether it is possible to change
OL,7,Fthe English mentality, Tuchel said:
OL,8,F"If it happens, then it has to be
OL,9,Fchanged.
OL,11,F"But I'm not sure, I always try to
OL,12,Fthink in football terms, in football
OL,13,Fmatters.
OL,15,F"I haven't seen the data yet, but I
OL,16,Fthink right after the goal, the
OL,17,Fmomentum swings completely in ball
OL,18,Fpossession, chances and it drops
OL,19,Fdramatically.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
