PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,F"We got too passive within our
OL,7,Fstructure. I tried to help, not to
OL,8,Fbecome more passive with a back five,
OL,9,Fbut to be more active, to be quicker
OL,10,Fout to the wingers, not to open up the
OL,11,Fgaps between the back four.
OL,13,F"We encouraged everyone to step out,
OL,14,Fto be more active within the
OL,15,Fstructure, but we just struggled.
OL,17,F"We couldn't find any duels any more,
OL,18,Fwhich was why we dropped deeper and
OL,19,Fdeeper, which was never the plan, but
OL,20,Fit happened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
