PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,F"We needed to get back on the ball;
OL,7,Fotherwise, you cannot break the
OL,8,Fpressure, and you cannot get the
OL,9,Fmomentum back.
OL,11,F"I think ball possession plays a
OL,12,Fcrucial role. It's maybe not in our
OL,13,FDNA like it is in the Spanish DNA or
OL,14,FArgentinian or Brazilian DNA to take
OL,15,Fthe ball, control the game and the
OL,16,Fball, which is also a big problem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@cO]
