OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,FThe German, who signed a contract
OL,7,Fthrough to 2028 ahead of the
OL,8,Ftournament, received the backing of
OL,9,Fthe Football Association and
OL,10,Freiterated his desire to lead England
OL,11,Finto a home European Championship.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Yes, 100 per cent. There is still
OL,19,Fenough to improve, and I am more than
OL,20,Fhappy to do that," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@RO]
