OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784294320
OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,F"I've loved it. I loved every day. I
OL,7,Fsaid after the Norway game that I see
OL,8,Fa disconnect from what I see in
OL,9,Ftraining on a football level and
OL,10,Fwithin the games, I think we can
OL,11,Fimpose ourselves more on the ball.
OL,13,F"I still think we can show how good
OL,14,Ffootball players we are. I think that
OL,15,Fis still in us, as I see it in
OL,16,Ftraining and in every camp.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
