OL,3,CNot in England's DNA to control game,
OL,4,Csays Tuchel after Argentina defeat
OL,6,F"And here also at the World Cup. I
OL,7,Fstill feel there is an extra level
OL,8,Fthat we need to conquer and need to
OL,9,Fstep up to the next level to get the
OL,10,Fbig prize."
